E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1425','51','','1','0','0','0','','','','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">佛山厨卫瓷砖价格如何？怎样选购厨卫瓷砖？很多人在进行新房装修时都会考虑这个问题。究竟怎样才能选择到好的厨卫瓷砖，让自己称心如意，感觉物有所值呢？首先我们先要了解佛山厨卫瓷砖的价格情况，在选择的时候根据自身的实际情况，选购合适的厨卫瓷砖。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">在选购前我们都会到实体店和上网查资料关于厨卫瓷砖价格和打听厨卫瓷砖多少钱，因此要特别注意厨卫瓷砖选购之前的问题。佛山瓷砖一线品牌厨卫瓷砖价格处于哪个水平呢？下面小编跟大家简单介绍一下。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">网络瓷砖第一品牌哈德逊厨卫釉面瓷砖价格</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13.8</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">元</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">片，东鹏瓷砖新锦绣系列厨卫釉面瓷砖价格</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">21.5</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">元</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">片，鹰牌防滑厨卫釉面瓷砖</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">16.7</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">元</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">片，诺贝尔厨卫釉面瓷砖</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">16</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">元</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">片。上述几个牌子都是佛山较知名的厨卫瓷砖品牌，其受欢迎程度在佛山都是名列前茅的。对于普通的家装，选择厨卫瓷砖可以选择上述几个品牌，物美价廉，质量也值得信赖。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align:center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2015-01-08/9cfc2ef1b57f3af0e3254bab66d14fb4.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">在选购厨卫瓷砖时，选择材质好的瓷砖才是最重要的。尤其是在装修厨卫的时候，因为厨卫的地面容易积水，容易造成打滑的现象，为了保证安全，选择瓷砖需要在粗糙度方面提高，需要加大摩擦力度，这样才能达到良好的防滑效果。目前市场上的瓷砖主要分为釉面砖和抛光砖。厨卫瓷砖大多使用釉面砖</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">最好选择材质好一点的。因为瓷砖装修与木地板装修不同</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">瓷砖重新装修很麻烦</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">最好是一次装修到位</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">千万不要因小失大。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">厨卫瓷砖价格如何以及对于厨卫瓷砖选购要把好关，</span> <span style=\\\\\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">需要提醒大家的是，多注意一些细节问题，就可以给全家人一个好的厨房，因此一定要慎之又慎，要注意在选购中多留些心眼，然后再确定是否购买。记住要为家人的健康负责。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">文章来源：哈德逊瓷砖编辑原创</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">转载请注明出处</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">http://www.hudsonhome.cn</span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1426','51','','1','0','0','0','','','','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">随着生活水平的提高，人们对家居的要求也越来越高，其中电视背景墙的装修是重头戏，在客厅的装修设计中，背景墙可以起到画龙点睛的作用，同时也能体现业主的审美观和个性。现在用于电视背景墙装饰的材料也越来越多，让大家的选择也多样化，如今市面上出现了一种新型的电视背景墙装饰材料&mdash;&mdash;微晶石，深受广大消费者所喜爱，品质好就是任性，打造高档家装，要选就选微晶石背景墙知名瓷砖品牌怎么样？</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">微晶石背景墙性能优良，经久耐磨。在生产过程中已经人为剔除了任何含辐射性的元素，同时可以生产出丰富多彩的色调系列，是现代最为安全的绿色环保型材料。所以是非常合适的电视背景墙装饰材料。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">由于背景墙在客厅的显要位置，最容易吸引人的眼球，巧妙利用各种材质进行多种组合，把电视背景墙打造成客厅的&ldquo;名片&rdquo;。很多中高端客户会选用微晶石背景墙。微晶石是陶瓷行业诞生的新品，其纹理清晰雅致，光泽柔和晶莹，色彩绚丽璀璨，质地坚硬细腻，受到中高端客户的亲睐，但是价格比较昂贵。一个普通背景墙利用微晶石材料至少要花费五万以上。在一些别墅高档住宅装修中，业主比较喜爱用微晶石来装修背景墙，因为微晶石能够彰显富丽堂皇的气质，能够显示主人的雍容华贵。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align:center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2015-01-08/81783e3c1d8aee1ff25a766eaa18fcc8.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"550\\\\\" height=\\\\\"380\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">对于微晶石品牌的选择，选择知名品牌最值得信赖。目前市场上比较活跃的微晶石品牌已经有不少，而且生产技术也相当成熟，其中比较有名的微晶石背景墙品牌有哈德逊、东鹏、欧神诺、马可波罗、诺贝尔等等，这些都是行业中的佼佼者，其产品也是集质量、美观于一体，是消费者值得放心选购的品牌。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">品质好就是任性。微晶石背景墙价格虽然昂贵，但想要打造高尚家装的消费者来说，微晶石背景墙呈现出的高端大气是其他任何装修材料无法比拟的，可以说是物有所值。而选择知名品牌微晶石背景墙，更能为家居锦上添花。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">文章来源：哈德逊瓷砖编辑原创</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">转载请注明出处</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">http://www.hudsonhome.cn</span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1427','51','','1','0','0','0','','','','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">洗手间瓷砖价格怎么样？洗手间装修瓷砖的选择是非常重要的。特别是洗手间地砖的选择，防滑性是我们不能忽略的因素。所以在选择洗手间瓷砖的时候不能只看外表美观，更重要的是质量，经久耐用才是硬道理。选购时需考虑周全，如果质量不过关就会造成日后的漏水现象，今天就给大家介绍一下洗手间瓷砖价格。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">洗手间进行铺贴时分为地砖和墙砖。因为洗手间本身的特殊性，在进行地砖和墙砖选择时也不尽相同，首先先说说洗手间墙砖的价格吧。贴墙砖是为了保护墙面免遭水溅的一种有效途径。用于洗手间的墙砖不但要美观、防潮和耐磨坚固。这种用于墙面装饰的墙砖一般分为两类：釉面砖和通体砖。墙砖的规格多种多样，主要有</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200mmx300mm</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">250mmx330mm</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200mmx280mm</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> 250mmx250mm</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300x300mm</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300x600mm</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">等等，洗手间墙砖价格也会因为品牌、规格和材质的不同，导致价格的差异。小编这里给大家罗列了佛山知名瓷砖品牌哈德逊瓷砖洗手间墙砖部分价格：</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300x450mm</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">的洗手间墙砖价格一般是</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">元</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">片</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,300x300mm</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">的洗手间墙砖价格是</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7.8</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">元</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">片，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300x600mm</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">的墙砖价格是</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">元</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">片。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align:center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2015-01-08/cc1d871c4a2082289c5c0bf288152cea.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"550\\\\\" height=\\\\\"450\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">对于洗手间地砖的选择，首要考虑其防滑性，洗手间接触到水的频率比较高，因此选择防滑性能较好的地砖可以确保家人安全。如果洗手间面积较大的话</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">一般用规格</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300x600mm</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">地砖，瓷砖价格</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">19.9</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">元</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">片。面积小一点的话可以用</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300x300mm</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">地砖，价格</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">元</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">/</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">片。如今市场上地砖种类众多</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">品牌不同</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">质量和价位不一，选择时一定要注重防滑。如果洗手间防滑做的不是很好，家里有老人和小孩就会威胁到他们的安全问题。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">因此，在选择洗手间瓷砖的时候，除了关注其价格之外，瓷砖的质量也很重要。洗手间环境一般都比较潮湿，墙砖的选择在美化洗手间的过程中占据了重要的地位。而地砖的选择对于保护家人安全也起着举足轻重的作用。由此可知，关于洗手间瓷砖的选择也是一门学问。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">文章来源：哈德逊瓷砖编辑原创</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">转载请注明出处</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">http://www.hudsonhome.cn</span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1428','51','','1','0','0','0','','','','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">现代人对家居格调的需求越来越多样化，欧式家居除了华丽、大气外，还散发着一丝丝古典的韵味，这深受业主们的追捧。只是要建造一个典雅、贵族的欧式家居并没有想象的那么容易，首先要考虑欧式家居选什么样的瓷砖好。因为瓷砖是家居的外衣，不同款式、颜色的瓷砖，装修出来的效果都不一样。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">欧式家居选什么样的瓷砖好</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">?</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">不同的瓷砖搭配到一起营造的格调不一样，可以从瓷砖款式、颜色、规格等方面进行考虑：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">瓷砖款式：如今市面上瓷砖款式众多，如微晶石、全抛釉、木纹砖、仿古砖、玻光砖等，仿古砖拥有古色古香的韵味，低调内敛却又不失华丽，是欧式家居不错的选择。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">瓷砖颜色：为了满足消费者多样的需要，很多佛山瓷砖品牌生产出各种颜色的瓷砖，如果要营造欧式格调的家居，可以选择淡黄色、砖红色、棕黄色的瓷砖。另外瓷砖色彩对人的视觉效果有影响，面积小的家居要选择简洁暗色调的瓷砖，让人有空间扩大的感觉。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align:center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2015-01-08/56e4ff12a52623b5ff02824da57fbfbe.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"550\\\\\" height=\\\\\"388\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">瓷砖规格：有些业主认为瓷砖越大，铺贴效果越大气，这是错误的观点。瓷砖规格应该根据空间大小来选择，一般</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">60</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">平的客厅可以选择</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">800</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">的瓷砖，而</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">60</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">平以下的客厅最好选择</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">600*600</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">、</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">500*500</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">、</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">450*450</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">的瓷砖。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">在考虑什么样的瓷砖好时，还要想到不同地方选购不一样的瓷砖，如长期有积水的卫浴、厨房，要选择防滑性强、吸水率低的瓷砖。当然还得考虑佛山哪个品牌瓷砖好，瓷砖质量不仅会影响铺贴效果，还会影响日常生活。佛山哈德逊瓷砖视产品质量为企业生命力，生产出质量上乘、时尚感强受消费者喜欢的瓷砖。哈德逊生产的</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">500*500</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">仿古砖，搭配上欧式家居，让家居独具欧式风情。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">文章来源：哈德逊瓷砖编辑原创</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">转载请注明出处</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">www.hudsonhome.cn</span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1429','51','','1','0','0','0','','','','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">受到双十一大促的刺激，如今很多企业都想搭上网销的顺风车，开启另一片新天地。在淘宝、天猫上淘东西已经成了人们的一种习惯，瓷砖企业在顺势而变，才能抢占更多的市场。网销会不会影响室内瓷砖价格</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">?</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">这是很多业主关注的问题。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">显然电商已经影响到我们生活的方方面面，网销瓷砖已经成了一种必然趋势，而且有不少企业已经步入了网销瓷砖的行列。网销瓷砖必然会影响室内瓷砖价格，网销少了铺租的压力折扣力度更大，尤其是活动期间价格更实惠，如双十二、双十一、九九大促、</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">618</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">等。当然价格也不可能无底洞地下降，毕竟瓷砖成本就是那么多。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">虽说很多企业都想利用好网络销售这把&ldquo;利剑&rdquo;，但总有大大小小的拦路虎出现。如物流运输、瓷砖质量、售后等问题。佛山高端瓷砖品牌要将这些问题处理好，才能让消费者对该企业的瓷砖更有信心。有些企业为了降低室内瓷砖价格、节约成本，降低窑炉温度，导致瓷砖硬度不够，易出现裂痕及破碎。物流运输问题应该是消费者最大的忧虑，瓷砖是易碎品，在运输过程中稍有不慎就会出现破碎等问题。为了打消业主们的忧虑，哈德逊瓷砖用中性纸箱包装产品</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">(</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">如果量多将打木托</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">)</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">，保障瓷砖完好、顺利地送达目的地。当然运输过程出现一些纰漏是正常的，如果出现破损的情况，可以拍照发给客服，客服将重新给您邮寄。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align:center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2015-01-08/4dc5aecc944c2c2c6d47957a749e7f79.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"550\\\\\" height=\\\\\"356\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">当然室内瓷砖价格不仅会受网销的影响，也会受成本、技术、品牌等因素的影响，业主们在买瓷砖时，应该先看瓷砖质量，再看瓷砖价格。尤其是在网上买瓷砖，既看不到瓷砖，又摸不到瓷砖，如果唯价格是论，很容易买到次品、赝品。在网上怎么买瓷砖好呢</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">?</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">首先要看网友的评价，如果有</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">80%</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">的好评就可以放心选购了</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">;</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">另外还要看销量跟品牌口碑。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">文章来源：哈德逊瓷砖编辑原创</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">转载请注明出处</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">www.hudsonhome.cn</span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1432','51','','1','0','0','0','','','','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">家装常用玻化砖哪个品牌好？随着社会发展、时代进步，人们生活水平不断提高，对家庭装修要求也逐渐提高。就像现在的女人，不仅要底子好，还要靠衣装，有了合适的衣服便能成为绝代佳人。家装也一样，要内外兼备，既要求合理的区间布局，又要硬件配备锦上添花，即使不能成就别墅豪宅也能装饰得小家碧玉、温馨舒适。根据家居装修瓷砖品牌需求，或选择奢华气派的微晶石、或选择雍容华贵的全抛釉、或选择古香古色的仿古砖、或购买简约大方的玻化砖&hellip;&hellip;根据不完全市场统计，其中玻化砖的需求量和使用量最大，下面针对玻化砖作一个全方位的解析。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">玻化砖是抛光砖的升级版，是表面经过打磨光亮成如镜面一样光滑的瓷砖，是经过高压压制、高温烧制而成的&ldquo;最硬瓷砖&rdquo;，并使用国际先进纳米技术完美解决了抛光砖气孔大导致防污性能低的缺点。因其在防污、防滑、耐磨方面超群出众，外表形象超凡脱俗，适用范围广泛，受到广大消费者喜爱。各瓷砖品牌更是各出奇招争相斗艳，成就其领域内的佼佼者。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">家装用玻化砖哪个品牌好？广东十大瓷砖品牌的哈德逊瓷砖在玻化砖上表现出类拔萃，其结合了中外市场需求，采用线上线下双渠道齐头并进的营销模式，以走量为准通过有效合理的方式为装修人们提供优质低价的玻化砖。其主打网络电子商务平台，通过流行、便利、可靠的网络交易平台使用瓷砖厂家直销的模式销售产品，给行业创造新的可行之路&ldquo;注入新鲜血液&rdquo;的同时为消费者提供高效的购砖形式。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align:center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2015-01-08/999927f35e21f68a5c4198afd23117fb.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"550\\\\\" height=\\\\\"379\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">哈德逊生产的玻化砖具有内在品质的同时美观大方，在物化性能上表现为防污防潮防滑、耐磨耐酸耐碱，在装饰性能上多以淡色为主，装修家居温馨自然、清新雅致，配搭家具可塑造欧式现代、中式现代、欧式古典、中式古典、日式、法式等一系列的风格，具有瓷砖界的&ldquo;万金油&rdquo;的美称。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">家装常用玻化砖哪个品牌好？其实在选择瓷砖品牌时多以瓷砖质量为核心，围绕质量选择合适的款式，再展开考虑其价格，再考察品牌服务，最终便能果断作出决定。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent:21.75pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">文章来源：哈德逊瓷砖编辑原创</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 30pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\\\\\">转载请注明出处</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">www.hudsonhome.cn</span></p>\r\n<!--EndFragment-->');");

